---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="SolidJS Dashboard" description="Real-time metrics dashboard built with SolidJS signals.">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 pt-32 pb-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <a href="/examples" class="text-sm text-brand-500 dark:text-brand-400 hover:underline">&larr; Back to Examples</a>
      <h1 class="mt-4 font-display text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        SolidJS <span class="gradient-text">Dashboard</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-2" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
        A real-time metrics dashboard with SolidJS signals and fine-grained reactivity.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <span class="rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">SolidJS</span>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">Signals</span>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">Charts</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div id="solid-dashboard-app" class="rounded-2xl p-8 themed-card">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl p-4 themed-card">
          <p class="text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">Requests/sec</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">12,847</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl p-4 themed-card">
          <p class="text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">Avg Latency</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-2xl font-bold text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">24ms</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl p-4 themed-card">
          <p class="text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">Error Rate</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400">0.02%</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl p-4 themed-card">
          <p class="text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">Uptime</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400">99.99%</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4 text-center text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">Add SolidJS integration for live reactive updates</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 rounded-xl p-6 themed-card">
      <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold">How it works</h2>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
        <li>- SolidJS signals for fine-grained reactivity without virtual DOM</li>
        <li>- <code class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">createSignal()</code> and <code class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">createEffect()</code></li>
        <li>- Real-time WebSocket data streaming</li>
        <li>- Lightweight chart rendering with Canvas API</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
